OL,5, A Londonderry couple whose daughter was
OL,6, born via a surrogate have said UK      
OL,7, surrogacy laws need to be simplified.  
OL,9,FPatrick and Jon Coyle's daughter, Wren,
OL,10,Fwas born in 2021. She was conceived by 
OL,11,FIVF and carried by Patrick's sister,   
OL,12,FCharley.                               
OL,14,FBut it has taken a further 18 months   
OL,15,Ffor the couple to be granted a parental
OL,16,Forder making them Wren's legal parents.
OL,18,F"It was a lot of back and forth so that
OL,19,Fwas a long time in the making," Jon    
OL,20,Ftold BBC Radio Foyle.                  
